trace_pow_card:
theorem zmod.trace_pow_card {p : ℕ} [fact p.prime] (M : matrix n n (zmod p)) : trace (M ^ p) = trace M ^ p :=
  by
  have h := finite_field.trace_pow_card M
  rwa [zmod.card] at h
#align zmod.trace_pow_card zmod.trace_pow_card
charpoly_pow_card:
@[simp]
theorem zmod.charpoly_pow_card {p : ℕ} [fact p.prime] (M : matrix n n (zmod p)) : (M ^ p).charpoly = M.charpoly :=
  by
  have h := finite_field.matrix.charpoly_pow_card M
  rwa [zmod.card] at h
#align zmod.charpoly_pow_card zmod.charpoly_pow_card
